:

1. U poenti* je da se uskladimo. (The point is to come to an agreement.)
2. Njegov argument nema poentu*. (His argument has no point.)
3. Činjenica je da je poenta* ovog predavanja da se nauče temelji. (The fact is that the point of this lecture is to learn the basics.)
4. Ne razumem poentu* njegove izjave. (I don't understand the point of his statement.)
5. Svi su razumeli poentu* njegovog govora. (Everyone understood the point of his speech.)